#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>In such situation, feel free to experiment with this database and then\n"
"                        to create a new one for your own usage.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ໃນສະຖານະການດັ່ງກ່າວ, ທ່ານສາມາດທົດລອງນຳໃຊ້ຖານຂໍ້ມູນນີ້ໄດ້ຕາມສະບາຍ ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນ\n"
"                        ສ້າງຖານຂໍ້ມູນໃໝ່ເພື່ອການນຳໃຊ້ຂອງທ່ານເອງ.</strong>"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Multiple resource blocking / period closure</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ການປິດກັ້ນຫຼາຍຊັບພະຍາກອນ / ການປິດຊ່ວງເວລາ</strong>"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
