#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Single resource blocking</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ການປິດກັ້ນຊັບພະຍາກອນດຽວ</strong>"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Use case</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ກໍລະນີການນຳໃຊ້</strong>"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:campsite.product_template_3
msgid ""
"A cozy spot for your tent or small camper, tucked away in the heart of the "
"forest or bathed in sunlight in a peaceful clearing. Perfect for an "
"intimate, close-to-nature getaway."
msgstr ""
"ບ່ອນທີ່ສະດວກສະບາຍສຳລັບເຕັ້ນ ຫຼື ລົດແຄ້ມຂະໜາດນ້ອຍຂອງທ່ານ, ເຊື່ອງຕົວຢູ່ໃນໃຈກາງປ່າ ຫຼື ທ່າມກາງແສງແດດໃ"
"ນບ່ອນທີ່ສະຫງົບ. ເໝາະສຳລັບການພັກຜ່ອນແບບໃກ້ຊິດກັບທຳມະຊາດ."

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_19
msgid "AA Batteries (4)"
msgstr "ຖ່ານ AA (4 ກ້ອນ)"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_20
msgid "AAA Batteries (4)"
msgstr "ຖ່ານ AAA (4 ກ້ອນ)"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Access to more details clicking the slot."
msgstr "ເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດເພີ່ມເຕີມໂດຍການຄລິກທີ່ຊ່ອງວ່າງ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add a line with Plancha or a Fan."
msgstr "ເພີ່ມລາຍການ ເຕົາປີ້ງ (Plancha) ຫຼື ພັດລົມ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add here as many of them as needed."
msgstr "ເພີ່ມຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້ໄດ້ຫຼາຍເທົ່າທີ່ຕ້ອງການ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add some products to the ongoing order and send it to the preparation display and\n"
"                bring them to your guests."
msgstr ""
"ເພີ່ມສິນຄ້າບາງຢ່າງເຂົ້າໃນລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ທີ່ກຳລັງດຳເນີນຢູ່ ແລະ ສົ່ງໄປຍັງໜ້າຈໍການກຽມພ້ອມ ແລະ\n"
"                ນຳໄປເສີບໃຫ້ແຂກຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjust the number of stars, leave a comment and send it!"
msgstr "ປັບຈຳນວນດາວ, ຂຽນຄຳຄິດເຫັນ ແລະ ກົດສົ່ງເລີຍ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Adjust the rental dates, click the book button and then proceed to checkout."
msgstr "ປັບວັນທີເຊົ່າ, ຄລິກປຸ່ມຈອງ ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນດຳເນີນການຊຳລະເງິນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjusting your offers in consequence"
msgstr "ປັບປຸງຂໍ້ສະເໜີຂອງທ່ານຕາມຄວາມເໝາະສົມ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Again, the <strong>Campsite App </strong>helps you manage the end of the "
"stay!"
msgstr ""
"ອີກຄັ້ງ, <strong>ແອັບ Campsite </strong>ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຈັດການຊ່ວງທ້າຍຂອງການພັກເຊົາໄດ້!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.custom_product_name
msgid "All Stay Offers"
msgstr "ຂໍ້ສະເໜີທີ່ພັກທັງໝົດ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternativelly, you can use the Front Desk from the POS App, selecting the\n"
"                    customer, adding any additional services and then paying with the customer\n"
"                    account. At the end of the stay the customer account will be charged as well."
msgstr ""
"ອີກທາງເລືອກໜຶ່ງ, ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ Front Desk ຈາກແອັບ POS, ໂດຍການເລືອກ\n"
"                    ລູກຄ້າ, ເພີ່ມບໍລິການເສີມຕ່າງໆ ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນຊຳລະດ້ວຍບັນຊີ\n"
"                    ລູກຄ້າ. ເມື່ອສິ້ນສຸດການພັກເຊົາ ບັນຊີລູກຄ້າຈະຖືກຮຽກເກັບເງິນເຊັ່ນກັນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively to individual resource blocking slots described earlier, you "
"can select a resource this leave applies to."
msgstr ""
"ນອກຈາກການປິດກັ້ນຊັບພະຍາກອນແບບແຍກສ່ວນທີ່ກ່າວມາກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້, ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເລືອກຊັບພະຍາກອນທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ກັບກາ"
"ນລານີ້ໄດ້."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, switch to the list view, and then change the resource.<br/>Be\n"
"                    careful not to double book a resource with such change!"
msgstr ""
"ອີກທາງເລືອກໜຶ່ງ, ປ່ຽນເປັນມຸມເບິ່ງແບບລາຍການ, ແລ້ວປ່ຽນຊັບພະຍາກອນ.<br/>ໃຫ້\n"
"                    ລະວັງຢ່າໃຫ້ມີການຈອງຊ້ຳຊ້ອນໃນຊັບພະຍາກອນດຽວກັນເມື່ອມີການປ່ຽນແປງ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, switch to the list view, which is more suitable if the booking is\n"
"                    not during the visualized date range and update the booking date range."
msgstr ""
"ອີກທາງເລືອກໜຶ່ງ, ປ່ຽນເປັນມຸມເບິ່ງແບບລາຍການ ເຊິ່ງຈະເໝາະສົມກວ່າຖ້າການຈອງ\n"
"                    ບໍ່ໄດ້ຢູ່ໃນຊ່ວງວັນທີທີ່ສະແດງຢູ່ ແລະ ອັບເດດຊ່ວງວັນທີການຈອງ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, type in the search bar and select the appropriate filter."
msgstr "ອີກທາງເລືອກໜຶ່ງ, ພິມໃສ່ແຖບຄົ້ນຫາ ແລະ ເລືອກຕົວຕອງທີ່ເໝາະສົມ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can create a slot as placeholder from the planning "
"directly:"
msgstr ""
"ອີກທາງເລືອກໜຶ່ງ, ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງຊ່ອງວ່າງເປັນບ່ອນຈອງໄວ້ກ່ອນຈາກການວາງແຜນໂດຍກົງ:"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "An automation is setup for an email to be sent automatically for you."
msgstr ""
"ມີການຕັ້ງຄ່າລະບົບອັດຕະໂນມັດເພື່ອໃຫ້ອີເມວຖືກສົ່ງອອກໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດສຳລັບທ່ານ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Any time you create a new survey and save it with the setting \"is customer satisfaction survey\", previous ones\n"
"                    will be archived so that it becomes your new default survey."
msgstr ""
"ທຸກຄັ້ງທີ່ທ່ານສ້າງແບບສຳຫຼວດໃໝ່ ແລະ ບັນທຶກດ້ວຍການຕັ້ງຄ່າ \"ແມ່ນແບບສຳຫຼວດຄວາມພຶງພໍໃຈຂອງລູກຄ້າ\", ແບບ"
"ສຳຫຼວດກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້\n"
"                    ຈະຖືກເກັບໄວ້ໃນບ່ອນເກັບມ້ຽນ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ອັນໃໝ່ກາຍເປັນແບບສຳຫຼວດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Anyone can create a portal account on your database.<br/>Open your website home page\n"
"                in a private tab to do so."
msgstr ""
"ໃຜກໍຕາມກໍສາມາດສ້າງບັນຊີພໍທໍ (portal) ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານໄດ້.<br/>ເປີດໜ້າທຳອິດຂອງເວັບໄຊຂອງທ່ານ\n"
"                ໃນແທັບສ່ວນຕົວ (private tab) ເພື່ອເຮັດສິ່ງນີ້."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "Are you considering a tentalo getaway?"
msgstr "ທ່ານກຳລັງຊອກຫາການພັກຜ່ອນແບບເຕັ້ນທາໂລ (tentalo) ຢູ່ບໍ່?"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Assign them a resource, which helps you keeping track."
msgstr "ກຳນົດຊັບພະຍາກອນໃຫ້ພວກເຂົາ ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຕິດຕາມໄດ້ງ່າຍຂຶ້ນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time during their stay, open their rental order from the Campsite "
"App."
msgstr ""
"ໃນທຸກເວລາລະຫວ່າງການພັກເຊົາຂອງພວກເຂົາ, ສາມາດເປີດລາຍການເຊົ່າໄດ້ຈາກແອັບ Campsite."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time from the guest order, use the Send message capability in the chatter\n"
"                    to exchange with your guest."
msgstr ""
"ໃນທຸກເວລາຈາກລາຍການສັ່ງຂອງແຂກ, ໃຊ້ຟັງຊັນ ສົ່ງຂໍ້ຄວາມ ໃນລະບົບສົນທະນາ (chatter)\n"
"                    ເພື່ອຕິດຕໍ່ສື່ສານກັບແຂກຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "At the end of their stay, your guests will pay for all those extras."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອສິ້ນສຸດການພັກເຊົາ, ແຂກຂອງທ່ານຈະຊຳລະສຳລັບຄ່າບໍລິການເສີມທັງໝົດເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Bar &amp; Restaurant and extra services"
msgstr "ບາ &amp; ຮ້ານອາຫານ ແລະ ບໍລິການເສີມ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Beyond daily operations, the Steering menu serves as the \"Captain’s "
"Bridge\" of your campsite. It provides a 500-day horizon to anticipate "
"market trends, manage risks, and optimize your revenue."
msgstr ""
"ນອກຈາກການດຳເນີນງານປະຈຳວັນແລ້ວ, ເມນູ Steering ຍັງເຮັດໜ້າທີ່ເປັນ \"ຫ້ອງບັນຊາການ\" ຂອງສະຖານທີ່"
"ຕັ້ງແຄ້ມຂອງທ່ານ. ມັນຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ເຫັນພາບລວມໃນໄລຍະ 500 ວັນ ເພື່ອຄາດການແນວໂນ້ມຕະຫຼາດ, ຈັດການຄວາມສ່ຽ"
"ງ ແລະ ເພີ່ມລາຍຮັບຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ສູງສຸດ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Blocking resources"
msgstr "ການປິດກັ້ນຊັບພະຍາກອນ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Booking a pitch"
msgstr "ການຈອງຈຸດກາງເຕັ້ນ"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_17
msgid "Bread"
msgstr "ເຂົ້າຈີ່"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.public.category,name:campsite.product_public_category_9
msgid "Bungalows"
msgstr "ບັງກາໂລ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a few products,\n"
"            sale orders and more."
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍການອັບໂຫຼດຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງຂອງໂມດູນນີ້, ຖານຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານຈະຖືກເຕັມໄປດ້ວຍສິນຄ້າບາງຢ່າງ,\n"
"            ລາຍການຂາຍ ແລະ ອື່ນໆ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.res_config_settings_form_view_inherited
msgid "Campsite"
msgstr "ສະຖານທີ່ຕັ້ງແຄ້ມ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "Carousel Indicator"
msgstr "ຕົວບົ່ງຊີ້ຮູບພາບສະໄລ້"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Charge your guests"
msgstr "ຮຽກເກັບເງິນຈາກແຂກຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:campsite.product_template_6
msgid ""
"Charming and compact, these A-frame cabins blend rustic style with modern "
"convenience. A snug retreat for couples or solo travelers looking for a "
"warm, sheltered stay in nature."
msgstr ""
"ເຮືອນພັກຊົງເອ (A-frame) ທີ່ມີສະເໜ່ ແລະ ກະທັດຮັດ, ປະສົມປະສານຮູບແບບພື້ນເມືອງເຂົ້າກັບຄວາມສະດວກສະບ"
"າຍທີ່ທັນສະໄໝ. ເປັນບ່ອນພັກຜ່ອນທີ່ອົບອຸ່ນສຳລັບຄູ່ຮັກ ຫຼື ຜູ້ທີ່ເດີນທາງຄົນດຽວ ທີ່ຊອກຫາບ່ອນພັກເຊົາທ່າມກາງທຳມະຊາ"
"ດ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "Check Out Out Stay Offers"
msgstr "ເບິ່ງຂໍ້ສະເໜີທີ່ພັກຂອງພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check guests in"
msgstr "ແຈ້ງແຂກເຂົ້າພັກ (Check-in)"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check guests out"
msgstr "ແຈ້ງແຂກອອກ (Check-out)"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check information and then confirm the booking."
msgstr "ກວດສອບຂໍ້ມູນ ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນຢືນຢັນການຈອງ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click one of the offers to book."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ຂໍ້ສະເໜີໃດໜຶ່ງເພື່ອຈອງ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Check in button to confirm they are now staying at your place!"
msgstr "ຄລິກປຸ່ມ ເຊັກອິນ ເພື່ອຢືນຢັນວ່າພວກເຂົາໄດ້ເຂົ້າພັກໃນສະຖານທີ່ຂອງທ່ານແລ້ວ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click the Check out button to capture they left their spot ."
msgstr "ຄລິກປຸ່ມ ເຊັກເອົ້າ ເພື່ອບັນທຶກວ່າພວກເຂົາໄດ້ອອກຈາກບ່ອນພັກແລ້ວ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click the Create Order to open the order form."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ ສ້າງລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ ເພື່ອເປີດແບບຟອມການສັ່ງຊື້."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Pay with demo button, and then Pay button to mimic the payment."
msgstr ""
"ຄລິກປຸ່ມ ຊຳລະດ້ວຍຕົວຢ່າງ, ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນກົດປຸ່ມ ຊຳລະເງິນ ເພື່ອຈຳລອງການຊຳລະເງິນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Settle PoS Orders button to add the corresponding order lines."
msgstr "ຄລິກປຸ່ມ ຈັດການລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ PoS ເພື່ອເພີ່ມລາຍການການສັ່ງຊື້ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the tail of the corresponding booking and drag it to the requested "
"date."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ສ່ວນທ້າຍຂອງການຈອງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ ແລະ ລາກໄປຫາວັນທີທີ່ຕ້ອງການ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Configure the email delay as you wish the email to be sent after the guest "
"checkout."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າໄລຍະເວລາການສົ່ງອີເມວຕາມທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການ ຫຼັງຈາກທີ່ແຂກເຊັກເອົ້າແລ້ວ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a new leave selecting the appropriate working schedule, the one from "
"your stay resources."
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງການລາໃໝ່ໂດຍເລືອກຕາຕະລາງການເຮັດວຽກທີ່ເໝາະສົມ, ເຊິ່ງແມ່ນອັນທີ່ມາຈາກຊັບພະຍາກອນທີ່ພັກຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a new leave the same way as previously, but this time specify the "
"resource this applies to."
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງການລາໃໝ່ໃນຮູບແບບດຽວກັນກັບກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້, ແຕ່ຄັ້ງນີ້ໃຫ້ລະບຸຊັບພະຍາກອນທີ່ຈະນຳໃຊ້ກັບການລານີ້."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Created offers are assigned no company nor branch (default behavior).<br/>As"
" a result, they are available from all companies and branches, as well as "
"all websites from those."
msgstr ""
"ຂໍ້ສະເໜີທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນຈະບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກກຳນົດໃຫ້ບໍລິສັດ ຫຼື ສາຂາໃດໜຶ່ງ (ເປັນຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ).<br/>ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, ພວກມັນຈຶ່ງສາມາດນ"
"ຳໃຊ້ໄດ້ໃນທຸກບໍລິສັດ ແລະ ສາຂາ, ລວມທັງທຸກເວັບໄຊຂອງພວກເຂົາ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Define start and end date time and save your leave."
msgstr "ກຳນົດວັນທີ ແລະ ເວລາເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ-ສິ້ນສຸດ ແລ້ວບັນທຶກການລາຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Deliver extra services"
msgstr "ໃຫ້ບໍລິການເສີມ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Discover more about Odoo by diving into our"
msgstr "ຄົ້ນຫາເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບ Odoo ໂດຍການເຂົ້າເບິ່ງ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Discover the basics of this package and explore all the possibilities Odoo offers to\n"
"            improve your experience."
msgstr ""
"ຄົ້ນຫາພື້ນຖານຂອງແພັກເກດນີ້ ແລະ ສຳຫຼວດທຸກຄວາມເປັນໄປໄດ້ທີ່ Odoo ມອບໃຫ້ເພື່ອ\n"
"            ປັບປຸງປະສົບການຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Don't be limited to those examples, you could have a paddles and kayaks "
"available or even bikes to rent!"
msgstr ""
"ຢ່າຈຳກັດພຽງແຕ່ຕົວຢ່າງເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ, ທ່ານສາມາດມີໄມ້ພາຍ ແລະ ເຮືອກາຍັກ ຫຼື ແມ່ນແຕ່ລົດຖີບໃຫ້ເຊົ່າກໍໄດ້!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Don't forget to save your setting changes."
msgstr "ຢ່າລືມບັນທຶກການປ່ຽນແປງການຕັ້ງຄ່າຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Don't forget to send them their invoice!"
msgstr "ຢ່າລືມສົ່ງໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ໃຫ້ພວກເຂົາ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"During an available period, click, drag and drop on a pitch line to create a"
" slot."
msgstr ""
"ໃນຊ່ວງເວລາທີ່ວ່າງ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກ, ລາກ ແລະ ວາງໃສ່ເສັ້ນຂອງຈຸດກາງເຕັ້ນເພື່ອສ້າງການຈອງ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Each company can have its own website!"
msgstr "ແຕ່ລະບໍລິສັດສາມາດມີເວັບໄຊຂອງຕົນເອງໄດ້!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Employee assignations"
msgstr "ການມອບໝາຍວຽກໃຫ້ພະນັກງານ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Employee would open the tasks from their hand and update the status until "
"Clean."
msgstr ""
"ພະນັກງານຈະເປີດເບິ່ງວຽກຈາກອຸປະກອນມືຖື ແລະ ອັບເດດສະຖານະຈົນກວ່າຈະເປັນ \"ສະອາດ (Clean)\"."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Enforcing weekly turnover"
msgstr "ການບັງຄັບໃຊ້ຮອບວຽນລາຍອາທິດ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Example: A bungalow for 2 is booked for 4 nights, two guests were here for the first\n"
"                    three nights but only one stayed the last night. Then the guest x nights is\n"
"                    2x3+1x1=7."
msgstr ""
"ບັງກາໂລສຳລັບ 2 ຄົນ ແມ່ນຖືກຈອງໄວ້ 4 ຄືນ, ແຂກສອງຄົນໄດ້ພັກຢູ່ນີ້ໃນ\n"
"                    ສາມຄືນທຳອິດ ແຕ່ມີພຽງຄົນດຽວທີ່ພັກໃນຄືນສຸດທ້າຍ. ດັ່ງນັ້ນ ຈຳນວນ \"ແຂກ x ຄື"
"ນ\" ແມ່ນ \n"
"                    2x3+1x1=7."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:campsite.product_template_5
msgid ""
"Experience the magic of camping with the comfort of a cozy cabin. Our "
"Tentalos combine the charm of sleeping under canvas with proper beds, "
"electricity, and stylish interiors."
msgstr ""
"ສຳຜັດກັບຄວາມມະຫັດສະຈັນຂອງການຕັ້ງແຄ້ມ ດ້ວຍຄວາມສະດວກສະບາຍຂອງເຮືອນພັກທີ່ອົບອຸ່ນ. ເຕັ້ນທາໂລ "
"(Tentalos) ຂອງພວກເຮົາໄດ້ລວມເອົາສະເໜ່ຂອງການນອນໃນເຕັ້ນ ເຂົ້າກັບຕຽງນອນທີ່ດີ, ໄຟຟ້າ ແລະ ການຕົກແ"
"ຕ່ງພາຍໃນທີ່ທັນສະໄໝ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "Explore Our Pitches Options"
msgstr "ສຳຫຼວດຕົວເລືອກຈຸດກາງເຕັ້ນຂອງພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_9
msgid "Fan"
msgstr "ພັດລົມ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid ""
"Fantastic staff! Always available and ready to help, they provide amazing "
"pitches and cabin! We loved the stay!"
msgstr ""
"ພະນັກງານດີຫຼາຍ! ພ້ອມໃຫ້ການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອຕະຫຼອດເວລາ, ພວກເຂົາມີຈຸດກາງເຕັ້ນ ແລະ ເຮືອນພັກທີ່ຍອດຢ້ຽມ! ພວກເ"
"ຮົາມັກການພັກເຊົານີ້ຫຼາຍ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "Find out more"
msgstr "ຊອກຫາລາຍລະອຽດເພີ່ມເຕີມ"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_10
msgid "Free Cancellation"
msgstr "ຍົກເລີກຟຣີ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From the <strong>Campsite App</strong>, you can manage your bookings.<br/>The\n"
"            Campsite App relies on the Rental and Planning Apps binding, with a few\n"
"            customizations."
msgstr ""
"ຈາກ <strong>ແອັບ Campsite</strong>, ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດການການຈອງຂອງທ່ານໄດ້.<br/>ແອັບ\n"
"            Campsite ອີງໃສ່ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ລະຫວ່າງແອັບ Rental (ການເຊົ່າ) ແລະ Planning (ການວ"
"າງແຜນ), ພ້ອມກັບການປັບແຕ່ງ\n"
"            ບາງສ່ວນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From the Roles sections, you can select the companies and branches this "
"employee shall have access to as well as the default one."
msgstr ""
"ຈາກພາກສ່ວນ Roles, ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກບໍລິສັດ ແລະ ສາຂາທີ່ພະນັກງານຜູ້ນີ້ສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງໄດ້ ລວມທັງກຳນົດອັນ"
"ທີ່ເປັນຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid ""
"From the initial inquiry to the check out, the team was incredibly "
"professional, friendly, and of good advice. I couldn't be happier with the "
"entire experience!"
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງແຕ່ການສອບຖາມຄັ້ງທຳອິດຈົນເຖິງການເຊັກເອົ້າ, ທີມງານມີຄວາມເປັນມືອາຊີບຫຼາຍ, ເປັນກັນເອງ ແລະ ໃຫ້ຄຳແນ"
"ະນຳທີ່ດີ. ຂ້ອຍມີຄວາມສຸກຫຼາຍກັບປະສົບການທັງໝົດນີ້!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From the search bar select the Today filter to see to check in and to check out\n"
"                orders."
msgstr ""
"ຈາກແຖບຄົ້ນຫາ ໃຫ້ເລືອກຕົວຕອງ \"ມື້ນີ້ (Today)\" ເພື່ອເບິ່ງລາຍການ\n"
"                ທີ່ຕ້ອງເຊັກອິນ ແລະ ເຊັກເອົ້າ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "From there you can add new companies."
msgstr "ຈາກບ່ອນນັ້ນ ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມບໍລິສັດໃໝ່ໄດ້."

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_18
msgid "Gaz Can 100g"
msgstr "ກະປ໋ອງແກັສ 100 ກຣາມ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:campsite.product_template_7
msgid ""
"Generous in size and comfort, these larger A-frame cabins offer space for "
"families or friends to unwind together. Enjoy a private, fully equipped "
"hideaway surrounded by nature."
msgstr ""
"ເຮືອນພັກຊົງເອ (A-frame) ຂະໜາດໃຫຍ່ທີ່ມີພື້ນທີ່ກວ້າງຂວາງ ແລະ ສະດວກສະບາຍ, ເໝາະສຳລັບຄອບຄົວ ຫຼື ກຸ່ມ"
"ໝູ່ເພື່ອນທີ່ຈະມາພັກຜ່ອນຮ່ວມກັນ. ເພີດເພີນກັບຄວາມເປັນສ່ວນຕົວ ພ້ອມອຸປະກອນຄົບຊຸດທ່າມກາງທຳມະຊາດ."

#. module: campsite
#: model:pos.category,name:campsite.pos_category_1
msgid "Goods"
msgstr "ສິນຄ້າ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Hello there!"
msgstr "ສະບາຍດີ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If not OK, then click the contact, fill in the Identity section and save the\n"
"                contact."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າຍັງບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກທີ່ລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່, ຕື່ມຂໍ້ມູນໃນສ່ວນຕົວຕົນ (Identity) ແລະ ບັນທຶກ\n"
"                ຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If they paid orders at any point of sale with their customer account, their "
"customer account due amount will be displayed as well as a button for you to"
" settle the associated orders."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າພວກເຂົາຊຳລະລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ຢູ່ຈຸດຂາຍ (POS) ໃດໜຶ່ງດ້ວຍບັນຊີລູກຄ້າ, ຍອດເງິນທີ່ຄ້າງຊຳລະໃນບັນຊີລູກຄ້າຈະຖືກ"
"ສະແດງຂຶ້ນ ພ້ອມກັບປຸ່ມເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານຈັດການລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If using the house keeping approver setting, designated\n"
"                    approvers can check each room and set their state to ready to close the tasks."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າໃຊ້ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຜູ້ອະນຸມັດການທຳຄວາມສະອາດ, ຜູ້ອະນຸມັດທີ່ຖືກກຳນົດ\n"
"                    ສາມາດກວດກາແຕ່ລະຫ້ອງ ແລະ ຕັ້ງສະຖານະເປັນ \"ພ້ອມ (ready)\" ເພື່ອປິດວຽ"
"ກໄດ້."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to execute a practical guided tour of this module, you should Import\n"
"                    demo data and try the Demo - Use Case (In the next Knowledge Article)"
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການລອງນຳໃຊ້ໂມດູນນີ້ຕາມຂັ້ນຕອນແນະນຳ, ທ່ານຄວນນຳເຂົ້າ\n"
"                    ຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ (demo data) ແລະ ລອງໃຊ້ Demo - Use Case (ໃນບົດຄວາມ "
"Knowledge ຖັດໄປ)"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you're not certain customers have ongoing bookings, before charging their"
" customer accounts, open their contact details from their menu (from the "
"customer list) and ask for the room they stay in<br/>Note: Their room is "
"listed in the Guests tab of their order."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານບໍ່ແນ່ໃຈວ່າລູກຄ່າມີການຈອງທີ່ກຳລັງດຳເນີນຢູ່ຫຼືບໍ່, ກ່ອນຈະຮຽກເກັບເງິນເຂົ້າບັນຊີລູກຄ້າ, ໃຫ້ເປີດລາຍລະອຽດ"
"ຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່ (ຈາກລາຍຊື່ລູກຄ້າ) ແລະ ສອບຖາມເລກຫ້ອງທີ່ພວກເຂົາພັກຢູ່<br/>ໝາຍເຫດ: ເລກຫ້ອງຂອງພວກເຂົາຈະຖືກ"
"ລະບຸໄວ້ໃນແທັບ ແຂກ (Guests) ຂອງລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "In any case, the resources are company and branch dependent."
msgstr "ໃນທຸກກໍລະນີ, ຊັບພະຍາກອນແມ່ນຂຶ້ນກັບບໍລິສັດ ແລະ ສາຂາ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In any case, you may have written records in journals which are not delete-able and which\n"
"            might be an issue for your traceability."
msgstr ""
"ໃນບາງກໍລະນີ, ທ່ານອາດຈະມີການບັນທຶກໃນສະໝຸດບັນຊີເຊິ່ງບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບໄດ້ ແລະ\n"
"            ອາດຈະເປັນບັນຫາສຳລັບການຕິດຕາມຂໍ້ມູນຄືນຫຼັງຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In case you outsource or rely more heavily on suppliers, the <strong>Purchase App</strong>\n"
"                will help you to manage those aspects."
msgstr ""
"ໃນກໍລະນີທີ່ທ່ານຈ້າງພາຍນອກ (outsource) ຫຼື ເພິ່ງພາຜູ້ສະໜອງເປັນຫຼັກ, <strong>ແອັບ Purchase (ການ"
"ຈັດຊື້)</strong>\n"
"                ຈະຊ່ວຍທ່ານຈັດການໃນສ່ວນນັ້ນໄດ້."

