msgstr "ຖັດໄປ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now that they relax, you can offer extra services to make your guests fill even more\n"
"            comfortable!"
msgstr ""
"ຕອນນີ້ພວກເຂົາໄດ້ພັກຜ່ອນແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດສະເໜີບໍລິການເສີມເພື່ອໃຫ້ແຂກຂອງທ່ານ\n"
"            ຮູ້ສຶກສະດວກສະບາຍຍິ່ງຂຶ້ນ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now that you have several companies or branches, you may want some of your "
"employees to access only to some of them in case they always work in some of"
" your places."
msgstr ""
"ຕອນນີ້ທ່ານມີຫຼາຍບໍລິສັດ ຫຼື ສາຂາແລ້ວ, ທ່ານອາດຈະຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ພະນັກງານບາງຄົນເຂົ້າເຖິງໄດ້ສະເພາະບາງບ່ອນ ໃ"
"ນກໍລະນີທີ່ພວກເຂົາເຮັດວຽກປະຈຳຢູ່ບ່ອນນັ້ນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odoo ມອບຄວາມເປັນໄປໄດ້ທີ່ບໍ່ມີຂີດຈຳກັດໃຫ້ແກ່ທ່ານ ເຊັ່ນ:"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this package. Feel free\n"
"            to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test everything around!"
msgstr ""
"ແນ່ນອນ, ນີ້ເປັນພຽງພາບລວມຂອງຟີເຈີທີ່ມີໃນແພັກເກດນີ້. ທ່ານສາມາດ\n"
"            ເພີ່ມແອັບໃໝ່, ລຶບ/ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ ແລະ ທົດລອງທຸກຢ່າງໄດ້ຕາມສະບາຍ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"On a daily basis, house keeping tasks are created depending\n"
"                    the current stays."
msgstr ""
"ໃນແຕ່ລະວັນ, ວຽກທຳຄວາມສະອາດຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍອີງຕາມ\n"
"                    ການພັກເຊົາທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນປະຈຸບັນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "On a resource to block line, click, drag and drop to create a slot."
msgstr ""
"ໃນແຖວຊັບພະຍາກອນທີ່ຈະປິດກັ້ນ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກ, ລາກ ແລະ ວາງເພື່ອສ້າງຊ່ວງເວລາປິດກັ້ນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "On the City Tax line, adjust the number of guest x nights delivered."
msgstr ""
"ໃນລາຍການພາສີທ້ອງຖິ່ນ (City Tax), ໃຫ້ປັບຈຳນວນ guest x nights ທີ່ໃຊ້ຕົວຈິງ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "On top of guest and stay management, you need to keep the place clean!"
msgstr ""
"ນອກຈາກການຈັດການແຂກ ແລະ ທີ່ພັກແລ້ວ, ທ່ານຍັງຕ້ອງຮັກສາຄວາມສະອາດຂອງສະຖານທີ່ນຳອີກ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid ""
"On top of the wonderful pitch we had, <br/>we love the kayaking experience "
"on the lake nearby. <br/>"
msgstr ""
"ນອກຈາກຈຸດກາງເຕັ້ນທີ່ຍອດຢ້ຽມແລ້ວ, <br/>ພວກເຮົາຍັງມັກປະສົບການການຂີ່ເຮືອກາຍັກຢູ່ໜອງນ້ຳໃກ້ໆນີ້ອີກດ້ວຍ. "
"<br/>"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Once confirmed, the payment is done and the order booked seamlessly!"
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອຢືນຢັນແລ້ວ, ການຊຳລະເງິນຈະສຳເລັດ ແລະ ການຈອງຈະຖືກບັນທຶກຢ່າງສະດວກສະບາຍ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once defined, you can switch between companies or branches from the company "
"selector at the top right of your screen.<br/>This will expose depending on "
"where you are, only the selected companies and branches data."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອກຳນົດແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດສະຫຼັບລະຫວ່າງບໍລິສັດ ຫຼື ສາຂາໄດ້ຈາກຕົວເລືອກບໍລິສັດຢູ່ມຸມຂວາເທິງຂອງໜ້າຈໍ.<br/>"
"ລະບົບຈະສະແດງສະເພາະຂໍ້ມູນຂອງບໍລິສັດ ແລະ ສາຂາທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once done adding all the necessary pitches, click on a recently added slot and then\n"
"                click the rental order link."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອເພີ່ມຈຸດກາງເຕັ້ນທີ່ຈຳເປັນທັງໝົດແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກໃສ່ຊ່ອງທີ່ຫາກໍ່ເພີ່ມ ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນ\n"
"                ຄລິກທີ່ລິ້ງລາຍການເຊົ່າ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once done, let's click, drag and drop on another pitch line to create a "
"slot."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອສຳເລັດແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກ, ລາກ ແລະ ວາງໃສ່ແຖວຈຸດກາງເຕັ້ນອື່ນເພື່ອສ້າງການຈອງ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Once done, logged in as a portal user."
msgstr "ເມື່ອສຳເລັດແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບໃນຖານະຜູ້ໃຊ້ພໍທໍ (portal user)."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once your guest order is all set after check out, create an invoice from "
"their order."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງແຂກຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າຮຽບຮ້ອຍແລ້ວຫຼັງຈາກເຊັກເອົ້າ, ໃຫ້ສ້າງໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ຈາກລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ນັ້ນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open a stay offer page from the website and scroll down to the Customer "
"Reviews section."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດໜ້າຂໍ້ສະເໜີທີ່ພັກຈາກເວັບໄຊ ແລະ ເລື່ອນລົງໄປທີ່ສ່ວນ ຄຳຕິຊົມຂອງລູກຄ້າ (Customer Reviews)."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open now, the Tasks from the accommodation app, House Keeping menu.<br/>This is\n"
"                the daily list of house keeping tasks to be tackled."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດເມນູ ວຽກ (Tasks) ຈາກແອັບທີ່ພັກ, ໃນສ່ວນ House Keeping.<br/>ນີ້ແມ່ນ\n"
"                ລາຍການວຽກທຳຄວາມສະອາດປະຈຳວັນທີ່ຕ້ອງຈັດການ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open one, assign it to an employee to plan the house keeping of the day."
msgstr "ເປີດວຽກໃດໜຶ່ງ, ມອບໝາຍໃຫ້ພະນັກງານເພື່ອວາງແຜນການທຳຄວາມສະອາດປະຈຳວັນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the <strong>Settings App</strong> and reach the companies from the menu"
" Users &amp; Companies."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດ <strong>ແອັບ Settings</strong> ແລະ ເຂົ້າໄປທີ່ບໍລິສັດຈາກເມນູ Users &amp; Companies."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the <strong>Settings App</strong> and reach the users from the menu "
"Users &amp; Companies."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດ <strong>ແອັບ Settings</strong> ແລະ ເຂົ້າໄປທີ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຈາກເມນູ Users &amp; Companies."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the <strong>Website App</strong> and navigate to the Stay Offers."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດ <strong>ແອັບ Website</strong> ແລະ ໄປທີ່ສ່ວນຂໍ້ສະເໜີທີ່ພັກ (Stay Offers)."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Board from the accommodation app, House Keeping menu.<br/>Here you have an\n"
"                overview of the cleanness state of your resources."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດກະດານຈາກແອັບທີ່ພັກ, ເມນູການອະນາໄມ.<br/>ຢູ່ທີ່ນີ້ ທ່ານຈະເຫັນ\n"
"                ພາບລວມກ່ຽວກັບສະຖານະຄວາມສະອາດຂອງຊັບພະຍາກອນຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Campsite App and navigate to the Configuration / Leaves menu."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດແອັບ Campsite ແລະ ໄປທີ່ເມນູ Configuration / Leaves (ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ / ການລາ)."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Campsite App and then navigate to the orders from the menu."
msgstr "ເປີດແອັບ Campsite ແລະ ໄປທີ່ເມນູລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ (Orders)."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Campsite App to appreciate the currently planned bookings with the\n"
"                Schedule."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດແອັບບ່ອນພັກແຮມ ເພື່ອເບິ່ງການຈອງທີ່ໄດ້ວາງແຜນໄວ້ໃນປັດຈຸບັນ \n"
"                ຜ່ານຕາຕະລາງ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the POS App and select one of the register, the Bar for example."
msgstr "ເປີດແອັບ POS ແລະ ເລືອກເຄື່ອງບັນທຶກເງິນໃດໜຶ່ງ, ເຊັ່ນ ບາ (Bar)."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Settings App and navigate to the Rental section or search for "
"\"Unavailability days\"."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດແອັບ Settings ແລະ ໄປທີ່ສ່ວນ Rental ຫຼື ຄົ້ນຫາ \"ວັນທີ່ບໍ່ວ່າງ (Unavailability days)\"."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Steering menu and select Availability."
msgstr "ເປີດເມນູ Steering ແລະ ເລືອກ ຄວາມວ່າງ (Availability)."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Steering menu and select Occupancy."
msgstr "ເປີດເມນູ Steering ແລະ ເລືອກ ອັດຕາການເຂົ້າພັກ (Occupancy)."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Survey App to find the customer satisfaction survey."
msgstr "ເປີດແອັບ Survey ເພື່ອຊອກຫາແບບສຳຫຼວດຄວາມພຶງພໍໃຈຂອງລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the door for more custom workflows and actions with the power of <strong>Studio\n"
"                App</strong>."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດໂອກາດສຳລັບຂັ້ນຕອນການເຮັດວຽກ ແລະ ການດຳເນີນການທີ່ປັບແຕ່ງໄດ້ຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນດ້ວຍພະລັງຂອງ <strong>ແອັ"
"ບ\n"
"                Studio</strong>."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the order of you just arrived guests."
msgstr "ເປີດລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງແຂກທີ່ຫາຊິມາຮອດ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open your guest order from the Campsite App."
msgstr "ເປີດລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງແຂກຈາກແອັບ Campsite."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Optimizing weekly turnover to maximize occupancy during peak season, you can"
" align your bookings to a weekly rental pattern (e.g., Saturday to "
"Saturday). By restricting check-ins and check-outs to specific days, you "
"synchronize your housekeeping and eliminate calendar gaps."
msgstr ""
"ການເພີ່ມຮອບວຽນລາຍອາທິດເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ອັດຕາການເຂົ້າພັກສູງສຸດໃນຊ່ວງລະດູທ່ອງທ່ຽວ, ທ່ານສາມາດປັບການຈອງໃຫ້"
"ເປັນແບບລາຍອາທິດ (ເຊັ່ນ: ວັນເສົາ ຫາ ວັນເສົາ). ໂດຍການຈຳກັດການເຊັກອິນ ແລະ ເຊັກເອົ້າໃນບາງມື້, ທ່ານ"
"ຈະສາມາດປະສານງານການທຳຄວາມສະອາດ ແລະ ຫຼຸດຜ່ອນຊ່ອງວ່າງໃນປະຕິທິນໄດ້."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Organize your employees' schedules with<font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> <strong>\n"
"                Planning</strong></font><strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> App</font>\n"
"                </strong><font class=\"text-o-color-5\">.</font>"
msgstr ""
"ຈັດລະບຽບຕາຕະລາງເວລາຂອງພະນັກງານຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍ<font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> <strong>"
"\n"
"                Planning</strong></font><strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> App</font>\n"
"                </strong><font class=\"text-o-color-5\">.</font>"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.public.category,name:campsite.product_public_category_11
msgid "Pitches"
msgstr "ຈຸດກາງເຕັ້ນ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Plan, check in and and check out bookings with the <strong>Campsite "
"App</strong>"
msgstr "ວາງແຜນ, ເຊັກອິນ ແລະ ເຊັກເອົ້າການຈອງດ້ວຍ <strong>ແອັບ Campsite</strong>"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_8
msgid "Plancha"
msgstr "ເຕົາປີ້ງ (Plancha)"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "Previous"
msgstr "ກ່ອນໜ້າ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Proceed to the payment with your terminal and set the invoice as paid."
msgstr ""
"ດຳເນີນການຊຳລະເງິນດ້ວຍເຄື່ອງຮູດບັດຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ຕັ້ງສະຖານະໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ເປັນ \"ຊຳລະແລ້ວ\"."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Promote your offers through the <strong>Website App</strong>"
msgstr "ໂຄສະນາຂໍ້ສະເໜີຂອງທ່ານຜ່ານ <strong>ແອັບ Website</strong>"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Reach us"
msgstr "ຕິດຕໍ່ພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Record guest identity"
msgstr "ບັນທຶກຕົວຕົນຂອງແຂກ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Recording the guest attendance is an obligation in numerous countries."
msgstr "ການບັນທຶກການມາພັກຂອງແຂກແມ່ນຂໍ້ບັງຄັບທາງກົດໝາຍໃນຫຼາຍປະເທດ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Save the order with those extra services."
msgstr "ບັນທຶກລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ພ້ອມກັບບໍລິການເສີມເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "See All"
msgstr "ເບິ່ງທັງໝົດ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "See all<span class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right ms-2\"/>"
msgstr "ເບິ່ງທັງໝົດ<span class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right ms-2\"/>"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Select one of your employee."
msgstr "ເລືອກພະນັກງານຄົນໃດໜຶ່ງຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Select or create a customer and then confirm the booking!"
msgstr "ເລືອກ ຫຼື ສ້າງລູກຄ້າໃໝ່ ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນຢືນຢັນການຈອງ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Setup company or branch specific offers when relevant."
msgstr "ຕັ້ງຄ່າຂໍ້ສະເໜີສະເພາະຂອງບໍລິສັດ ຫຼື ສາຂາ ເມື່ອມີຄວາມກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Share your stay offers across your companies and branches (default "
"behavior);"
msgstr ""
"ແບ່ງປັນຂໍ້ສະເໜີທີ່ພັກຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ກັບທຸກບໍລິສັດ ແລະ ສາຂາ (ເປັນຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ);"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_6
msgid "Small Bungalow (up to 4 pers.)"
msgstr "ບັງກາໂລຂະໜາດນ້ອຍ (ພັກໄດ້ສູງສຸດ 4 ຄົນ)"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_3
msgid "Small Pitch"
msgstr "ຈຸດກາງເຕັ້ນຂະໜາດນ້ອຍ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:campsite.product_template_4
msgid ""
"Spacious and comfortable, these pitches welcome bigger tents, caravans, or "
"motorhomes. Set in tranquil forest shade or open clearings, they’re ideal "
"for families or groups seeking extra room to relax."
msgstr ""
"ຈຸດກາງເຕັ້ນທີ່ກວ້າງຂວາງ ແລະ ສະດວກສະບາຍ, ເໝາະສຳລັບເຕັ້ນຂະໜາດໃຫຍ່, ລົດຄາລາວານ ຫຼື ລົດມໍເຕີໂຮມ. "
"ຕັ້ງຢູ່ໃນຮົ່ມໄມ້ທີ່ງຽບສະຫງົບ ຫຼື ໃນທົ່ງພຽງທີ່ໂລ່ງແຈ້ງ, ເໝາະສຳລັບຄອບຄົວ ຫຼື ກຸ່ມທີ່ຕ້ອງການພື້ນທີ່ພັກຜ່ອນເພີ່ມເຕີມ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Still from the Campsite App Schedule, simply drag and drop a booking to "
"another offer, from small pitch to large pitch for example!"
msgstr ""
"ຍັງຢູ່ໃນສ່ວນຕາຕະລາງຂອງແອັບ Campsite, ທ່ານພຽງແຕ່ລາກ ແລະ ວາງການຈອງໄປຫາຂໍ້ສະເໜີອື່ນ, ເຊັ່ນ: ຈາ"
"ກຈຸດກາງເຕັ້ນຂະໜາດນ້ອຍ ໄປຫາຂະໜາດໃຫຍ່!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Still from their Rental Order, open the Guests tab."
msgstr "ຍັງຢູ່ໃນລາຍການເຊົ່າຂອງພວກເຂົາ, ໃຫ້ເປີດແທັບ ແຂກ (Guests)."

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.template,name:campsite.product_template_5
msgid "Tentalo"
msgstr "ເຕັ້ນທາໂລ (Tentalo)"

#. module: campsite
#: model:product.public.category,name:campsite.product_public_category_10
msgid "Tentalos"
msgstr "ເຕັ້ນທາໂລ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Gantt chart is color-coded to reflect on the availability for you to "
"work on filling in."
msgstr ""
"ແຜນພູມ Gantt ມີການໃຊ້ລະຫັດສີເພື່ອສະແດງເຖິງຄວາມວ່າງ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດການການຈອງໃຫ້ເຕັມໄດ້."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Gantt chart is color-coded to reflect on the occupancy, the higher the "
"better."
msgstr ""
"ແຜນພູມ Gantt ມີການໃຊ້ລະຫັດສີເພື່ອສະແດງເຖິງອັດຕາການເຂົ້າພັກ, ຍິ່ງສູງຍິ່ງດີ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Occupancy view allows you to visualize your \"Sales Success\". It "
"answers one simple question: <i>How well am I filling my campsite?</i>"
msgstr ""
"ມຸມເບິ່ງອັດຕາການເຂົ້າພັກ (Occupancy) ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານເຫັນພາບລວມຂອງ \"ຄວາມສຳເລັດໃນການຂາຍ\". ມັນຕ"
"ອບຄຳຖາມງ່າຍໆວ່າ: <i>ຂ້ອຍຈັດການໃຫ້ແຂກເຂົ້າພັກໃນແຄ້ມໄດ້ເຕັມດີປານໃດ?</i>"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid ""
"The feeling of freedom with the comfort of a cabin!<br/>We'll guide you "
"through the options and help you choose the perfect fit for your getaway. "
"<br/> You can decide freely whether to proceed with your booking."
msgstr ""
"ຄວາມຮູ້ສຶກມີອິດສະຫຼະພ້ອມກັບຄວາມສະດວກສະບາຍຂອງເຮືອນພັກ!<br/>ພວກເຮົາຈະແນະນຳຕົວເລືອກຕ່າງໆ ແລະ ຊ່"
"ວຍທ່ານເລືອກສິ່ງທີ່ເໝາະສົມທີ່ສຸດສຳລັບການພັກຜ່ອນຂອງທ່ານ. <br/> ທ່ານສາມາດຕັດສິນໃຈໄດ້ຢ່າງອິດສະຫຼະວ່າຈະດ"
"ຳເນີນການຈອງຕໍ່ຫຼືບໍ່."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The strength of Odoo is to separate the accounting and many other aspects "
"which are company dependent!"
msgstr ""
"ຈຸດແຂງຂອງ Odoo ແມ່ນການແຍກລະບົບບັນຊີ ແລະ ຫຼາຍພາກສ່ວນອື່ນໆ ໃຫ້ຂຶ້ນກັບແຕ່ລະບໍລິສັດຢ່າງເປັນເອກະລາດ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Then set the days during which you want to prevent check in and check out to"
" take place, ex. All days but Saturday"
msgstr ""
"ຈາກນັ້ນກຳນົດມື້ທີ່ທ່ານບໍ່ຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ມີການເຊັກອິນ ແລະ ເຊັກເອົ້າ, ເຊັ່ນ: ທຸກມື້ຍົກເວັ້ນວັນເສົາ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr ""
"ທັງໝົດນີ້ແມ່ນລວມຢູ່ໃນການສະໝັກໃຊ້ປະຈຸບັນຂອງທ່ານໂດຍບໍ່ມີຄ່າໃຊ້ຈ່າຍເພີ່ມ; ສຳຫຼວດໄດ້ຕາມສະບາຍ! 🙃"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"They as well share the same pricing, defined at the stay offer level, which "
"has its pros and cons."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຂົາຍັງໃຊ້ລາຄາດຽວກັນ, ເຊິ່ງກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນລະດັບຂໍ້ສະເໜີທີ່ພັກ, ເຊິ່ງມີທັງຂໍ້ດີ ແລະ ຂໍ້ເສຍ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "They want multiple pitches?"
msgstr "ພວກເຂົາຕ້ອງການຈອງຫຼາຍຈຸດກາງເຕັ້ນບໍ່?"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "They were happy about their stay, let's ask them to leave a review."
msgstr "ພວກເຂົາມີຄວາມສຸກກັບການພັກເຊົາ, ມາຂໍໃຫ້ພວກເຂົາຊ່ວຍຂຽນລີວິວກັນເລີຍ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "They will balance their customer account during the check out!"
msgstr "ພວກເຂົາຈະຊຳລະຍອດເງິນທີ່ຄ້າງໃນບັນຊີລູກຄ້າໃນລະຫວ່າງການເຊັກເອົ້າ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This blocks simulataneously all resources related to this working schedule "
"during the prescribed period."
msgstr ""
"ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະປິດກັ້ນທຸກຊັບພະຍາກອນທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບຕາຕະລາງການເຮັດວຽກນີ້ພ້ອມກັນ ໃນຊ່ວງເວລາທີ່ກຳນົດ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This setup is relevant in case of place specific offers or when pricing "
"varies between places."
msgstr ""
"ການຕັ້ງຄ່ານີ້ແມ່ນກ່ຽວຂ້ອງໃນກໍລະນີທີ່ມີຂໍ້ສະເໜີສະເພາະບ່ອນ ຫຼື ເມື່ອລາຄາແຕກຕ່າງກັນລະຫວ່າງແຕ່ລະສະຖານທີ່."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This time click the Add to last order button to add this pitch to the booking and\n"
"                voila!"
msgstr ""
"ຄັ້ງນີ້ໃຫ້ຄລິກປຸ່ມ ເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ຫຼ້າສຸດ ເພື່ອເພີ່ມຈຸດກາງເຕັ້ນນີ້ເຂົ້າໃນການຈອງ ແລະ\n"
"                ຮຽບຮ້ອຍ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This time, simply leave a note about the why this is booked and save the "
"slot."
msgstr ""
"ຄັ້ງນີ້, ພຽງແຕ່ຂຽນບັນທຶກເຫດຜົນວ່າເປັນຫຍັງຈຶ່ງຈອງບ່ອນນີ້ໄວ້ ແລະ ບັນທຶກຊ່ອງການຈອງ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Those city tax are now due as well as any other additional services consumed during the\n"
"            stay."
msgstr ""
"ພາສີທ້ອງຖິ່ນເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນເຖິງກຳນົດຊຳລະແລ້ວ ລວມທັງບໍລິການເສີມອື່ນໆ ທີ່ຖືກນຳໃຊ້ໃນລະຫວ່າງ\n"
"            ການພັກເຊົາ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To ensure your guests no longer receive the satisfaction survey, you can "
"easily archive it at any time."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນວ່າແຂກຂອງທ່ານຈະບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບແບບສຳຫຼວດຄວາມພຶງພໍໃຈອີກ, ທ່ານສາມາດເກັບມັນໄວ້ໃນບ່ອນເກັບມ້ຽນ "
"(archive) ໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍທຸກເວລາ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Trace guest attendance"
msgstr "ຕິດຕາມການມາພັກຂອງແຂກ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Two options are now available to you with multiple companies and branches:"
msgstr "ຕອນນີ້ມີສອງຕົວເລືອກໃຫ້ທ່ານນຳໃຊ້ກັບລະບົບຫຼາຍບໍລິສັດ ແລະ ສາຂາ:"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Type in the customer name in the Schedule search bar filtering by Customer."
msgstr ""
"ພິມຊື່ລູກຄ້າໃສ່ໃນແຖບຄົ້ນຫາຂອງຕາຕະລາງ (Schedule) ໂດຍຕອງຕາມ ລູກຄ້າ (Customer)."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid ""
"We offer small and large pitches, in the heart of the forest, in clearings "
"and in fields."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາມີຈຸດກາງເຕັ້ນທັງຂະໜາດນ້ອຍ ແລະ ຂະໜາດໃຫຍ່, ບໍ່ວ່າຈະເປັນໃນໃຈກາງປ່າ, ໃນທົ່ງພຽງ ຫຼື ໃນທົ່ງຫຍ້າ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Welcome your guests as well from the <strong>Campsite App</strong>."
msgstr "ຕ້ອນຮັບແຂກຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ເຊັ່ນກັນຈາກ <strong>ແອັບ Campsite</strong>."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "When all is in order, confirm their invoice for payment."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທຸກຢ່າງຮຽບຮ້ອຍແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ຢືນຢັນໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ຂອງພວກເຂົາເພື່ອຊຳລະເງິນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When creating an offer, assign them a company or a branch.<br/>As a result, "
"they are available only for the selected company or branch, and will be "
"available only from its website."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອສ້າງຂໍ້ສະເໜີ, ໃຫ້ກຳນົດບໍລິສັດ ຫຼື ສາຂາໃຫ້ພວກມັນ.<br/>ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, ພວກມັນຈະສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ໄດ້ສະເພາະໃນບໍລິ"
"ສັດ ຫຼື ສາຂາທີ່ເລືອກເທົ່ານັ້ນ, ແລະ ຈະສະແດງສະເພາະໃນເວັບໄຊຂອງບ່ອນນັ້ນ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When they ask for the bill, you can charge them directly or add the bill to their\n"
"                customer account.<br/>To do so, open the corresponding order from the table or from\n"
"                the order list and select the customer to charge.<br/>Click the payment and the\n"
"                validation buttons!"
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອພວກເຂົາຂໍໃບບິນ, ທ່ານສາມາດຮຽກເກັບເງິນໂດຍກົງ ຫຼື ເພີ່ມໃບບິນເຂົ້າໃນບັນຊີ\n"
"                ລູກຄ້າຂອງພວກເຂົາ.<br/>ເພື່ອເຮັດແນວນັ້ນ, ໃຫ້ເປີດລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງຈາກໂຕະ "
"ຫຼື ຈາກ\n"
"                ລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ ແລະ ເລືອກລູກຄ້າທີ່ຈະຮຽກເກັບເງິນ.<br/>ຄລິກປຸ່ມການຊຳລະເງິນ ແລະ ປຸ່"
"ມ\n"
"                ຢືນຢັນ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid "Where every stay becomes a retreat."
msgstr "ບ່ອນທີ່ທຸກການພັກເຊົາກາຍເປັນການພັກຜ່ອນຢ່ອນໃຈ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"While Occupancy focuses on what is full, the Availability view focuses on "
"what is left to sell. It is your primary tool for operational safety and "
"\"Scarcity Pricing.\""
msgstr ""
"ໃນຂະນະທີ່ອັດຕາການເຂົ້າພັກ (Occupancy) ເນັ້ນໃສ່ສິ່ງທີ່ເຕັມແລ້ວ, ມຸມເບິ່ງຄວາມວ່າງ (Availability) ຈ"
"ະເນັ້ນໃສ່ສິ່ງທີ່ຍັງເຫຼືອໃຫ້ຂາຍ. ມັນແມ່ນເຄື່ອງມືຫຼັກຂອງທ່ານສຳລັບຄວາມປອດໄພໃນການດຳເນີນງານ ແລະ \"ການຕັ້ງ"
"ລາຄາຕາມຄວາມຕ້ອງການສູງ\""

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Willing to upgrade a booking?"
msgstr "ຕ້ອງການອັບເກຣດການຈອງບໍ່?"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.homepage
msgid ""
"With just a click, planning your perfect camping escape has never been "
"simpler.<br/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"ພຽງແຕ່ຄລິກດຽວ, ການວາງແຜນການພັກຜ່ອນຕັ້ງແຄ້ມທີ່ສົມບູນແບບຂອງທ່ານກໍຈະງ່າຍກວ່າທີ່ເຄີຍ.<br/><br/>"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With the create slot for this resource, no overlapping booking slot would be"
" created.<br/>Care about the start and end time or this blockage to make to "
"re-open when suited."
msgstr ""
"ດ້ວຍການສ້າງຊ່ອງວ່າງສຳລັບຊັບພະຍາກອນນີ້, ຈະບໍ່ມີການສ້າງການຈອງທີ່ຊ້ຳຊ້ອນກັນ.<br/>ກະລຸນາກວດສອບເວລາເ"
"ລີ່ມຕົ້ນ ແລະ ສິ້ນສຸດຂອງການປິດກັ້ນນີ້ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ສາມາດເປີດນຳໃຊ້ຄືນໄດ້ເມື່ອເຖິງເວລາ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງການປຶກສາຫາລືກ່ຽວກັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານກັບພວກເຮົາ ຫຼື ຕ້ອງການໄປໃຫ້ໄກກວ່ານີ້ບໍ່?"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "You Campsite is online and future guests found it!"
msgstr "ສະຖານທີ່ຕັ້ງແຄ້ມຂອງທ່ານອອນໄລນ໌ແລ້ວ ແລະ ແຂກໃນອະນາຄົດໄດ້ຄົ້ນພົບມັນແລ້ວ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You are repairing a bungalow or simply welcoming family and don't want "
"guests to book it?<br/>Alternatively, you are closing for a week during an "
"inter season break?<br/>Let's have this reflected in your schedule!"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານກຳລັງສ້ອມແປງບັງກາໂລ ຫຼື ພຽງແຕ່ຕ້ອງການຕ້ອນຮັບຄອບຄົວ ແລະ ບໍ່ຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ແຂກຈອງ?<br/>ຫຼື ທ່ານກຳລັ"
"ງຈະປິດເປັນເວລາໜຶ່ງອາທິດໃນຊ່ວງພັກລະດູການ?<br/>ມາສະແດງສິ່ງເຫຼົ່ານີ້ໃນຕາຕະລາງຂອງທ່ານກັນເລີຍ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງທຸກແອັບທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຈາກໜ້າຈໍຫຼັກ (dashboard)."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can as well select your company and in the Branches tab define branches."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເລືອກບໍລິສັດຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ກຳນົດສາຂາໄດ້ໃນແທັບ ສາຂາ (Branches)."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can find the participants and answers from the smart buttons of the "
"survey."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເບິ່ງລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ເຂົ້າຮ່ວມ ແລະ ຄຳຕອບໄດ້ຈາກປຸ່ມລັດ (smart buttons) ຂອງແບບສຳຫຼວດ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt your\n"
"                    Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ສຳເລັດກໍລະນີຕົວຢ່າງນັ້ນແລ້ວ! ຍັງມີອີກຫຼາຍລ້ານວິທີທີ່ຈະປັບປຸງການຕັ້ງຄ່າ\n"
"                    Odoo ຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງທຸລະກິດ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You could customize this section to add the identity document picture or extra\n"
"                    fields at your convenience with studio. Just be careful, such customizations can\n"
"                    quickly become messy."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດປັບແຕ່ງສ່ວນນີ້ເພື່ອເພີ່ມຮູບພາບເອກະສານຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນ ຫຼື ເພີ່ມ\n"
"                    ຂໍ້ມູນອື່ນໆ ໄດ້ຕາມຄວາມສະດວກດ້ວຍ Studio. ແຕ່ຕ້ອງລະວັງ, ການປັບແຕ່ງດັ່ງກ່າວ"
"ອາດ\n"
"                    ເຮັດໃຫ້ລະບົບສັບສົນໄດ້ຖ້າບໍ່ວາງແຜນໃຫ້ດີ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries &gt;\n"
"                    Upgrade your package and check the related box"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງບໍ? ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ຢູ່. ໃຫ້ໄປທີ່ ແອັບ &gt; Industries &gt;\n"
"                    Upgrade your package ແລະ ໝາຍເອົາຊ່ອງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "You have a future guest on the line willing to book a pitch?"
msgstr "ທ່ານມີແຂກທີ່ກຳລັງຕິດຕໍ່ສອບຖາມເພື່ອຈອງຈຸດກາງເຕັ້ນບໍ່?"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You have an Campsite but may be providing numerous peripheral services and offers.<br/>Here\n"
"            is how you might centralize those and bind them to your customers in a single database."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານມີສະຖານທີ່ຕັ້ງແຄ້ມ ແຕ່ອາດຈະມີການໃຫ້ບໍລິການເສີມ ແລະ ຂໍ້ສະເໜີອື່ນໆ ຢ່າງຫຼວງຫຼາຍ.<br/>ນີ້ແມ່ນ\n"
"            ວິທີທີ່ທ່ານສາມາດລວມສິ່ງເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນເຂົ້າກັນ ແລະ ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ພວກມັນກັບລູກຄ້າຂອງທ່ານໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນດຽວ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for Campsite package. By doing so, we have installed a\n"
"            bunch of necessary apps to run your business efficiently."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຫາກໍ່ຕິດຕັ້ງແພັກເກດ Odoo ສຳລັບ Campsite. ໂດຍການເຮັດສິ່ງນີ້, ພວກເຮົາໄດ້ຕິດຕັ້ງ\n"
"            ບັນດາແອັບທີ່ຈຳເປັນເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານດຳເນີນທຸລະກິດໄດ້ຢ່າງມີປະສິດທິພາບ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You may be running multiple places at the same time and most likely be "
"willing to run them all from the same database.<b/>We got you covered with "
"this using multiple companies or branches!"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານອາດຈະດຳເນີນການຫຼາຍສະຖານທີ່ໃນເວລາດຽວກັນ ແລະ ຕ້ອງການຈັດການທັງໝົດນັ້ນຈາກຖານຂໍ້ມູນດຽວກັນ.<b/>"
"ພວກເຮົາໄດ້ກຽມລະບົບຮອງຮັບໄວ້ແລ້ວ ໂດຍການນຳໃຊ້ຫຼາຍບໍລິສັດ ຫຼື ສາຂາ!"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You may have noticed the city tax were added to the guest order from the moment they\n"
"            checked in.<br/>This is because city taxes are to be billed to spent nights in practice\n"
"            and not in theory.<br/>Let's adjust them now."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານອາດຈະສັງເກດເຫັນວ່າພາສີທ້ອງຖິ່ນ (city tax) ຖືກເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງແຂກຕັ້ງແຕ່ຕອນທີ່ພວກເຂົ"
"າ\n"
"            ເຊັກອິນ.<br/>ນັ້ນກໍຍ້ອນວ່າໃນທາງປະຕິບັດ, ພາສີທ້ອງຖິ່ນຈະຖືກເກັບຕາມຈຳນວນຄືນທີ່ພັກຈິງ\n"
"            ບໍ່ແມ່ນຕາມທິດສະດີ.<br/>ພວກເຮົາມາປັບປຸງພວກມັນຕອນນີ້ເລີຍ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid "You might have tested this package with or without demo data."
msgstr "ທ່ານອາດຈະໄດ້ທົດລອງໃຊ້ແພັກເກດນີ້ທັງແບບມີ ຫຼື ບໍ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ."

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You noticed that the Identity Check highlights whether you captured all the\n"
"            necessary information for a guest?"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສັງເກດເຫັນບໍ່ວ່າ ລະບົບກວດສອບຕົວຕົນ (Identity Check) ຈະສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນວ່າທ່ານໄດ້ບັນທຶກ\n"
"            ຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຈຳເປັນທັງໝົດຂອງແຂກແລ້ວຫຼືບໍ່?"

#. module: campsite
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campsite.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You now know how to create a new order.<br/>Let's replicate the previous steps but\n"
